      "text": "4. Sliding window counter\nSliding window log + fixed window counter\nguestimates how many requests would be pending\n\n\nlets say,\n6 requests in last 30 seconds, so 4 requests can be made in next 30 seconds",
      "fontSize": 20,
      "fontFamily": 5,
      "textAlign": "left",
      "verticalAlign": "top",
      "containerId": null,
      "originalText": "4. Sliding window counter\nSliding window log + fixed window counter\nguestimates how many requests would be pending\n\n\nlets say,\n6 requests in last 30 seconds, so 4 requests can be made in next 30 seconds",
      "autoResize": true,
      "lineHeight": 1.25
    },
