      "index": "b2w",
      "roundness": null,
      "seed": 1013622214,
      "version": 233,
      "versionNonce": 1262721734,
      "isDeleted": true,
      "boundElements": [
        {
          "id": "_p-DBMT2mot8ctuvpoxr1",
          "type": "arrow"
        }
      ],
      "updated": 1781363287135,
      "link": null,
      "locked": false,
      "text": "Consistent Hashing\n\nFor partitioning we use \nHash \n\nkey % n = \nSHA5 kind of algorithm\n\nProblem:\nWhat happens when servers are added or removed?\nWe need to rebalance all the keys\n\nSoln:\nConsistent hashing\n\n",
      "fontSize": 20,
      "fontFamily": 5,
      "textAlign": "left",
      "verticalAlign": "top",
      "containerId": null,
      "originalText": "Consistent Hashing\n\nFor partitioning we use \nHash \n\nkey % n = \nSHA5 kind of algorithm\n\nProblem:\nWhat happens when servers are added or removed?\nWe need to rebalance all the keys\n\nSoln:\nConsistent hashing\n\n",
      "autoResize": true,
      "lineHeight": 1.25
    },
