      "index": "b3L",
      "roundness": null,
      "seed": 1440929542,
      "version": 295,
      "versionNonce": 610976794,
      "isDeleted": true,
      "boundElements": null,
      "updated": 1781363287135,
      "link": null,
      "locked": false,
      "text": "Solution : Virtual Nodes (VNodes)\nCreate 100 virtual nodes for each server and hash them, they spread across and \neven the distribution\n\nDistributed Databases\n- Cassandra\n- DynamoDB\n- Riak\nDistributed Caches\n- Redis Clusters\n- Memcached Clusters\nLoad Balancing\n- Service routing\n- Request distribution\nCDNs\n- Edge server assignment",
      "fontSize": 20,
      "fontFamily": 5,
      "textAlign": "left",
      "verticalAlign": "top",
      "containerId": null,
      "originalText": "Solution : Virtual Nodes (VNodes)\nCreate 100 virtual nodes for each server and hash them, they spread across and \neven the distribution\n\nDistributed Databases\n- Cassandra\n- DynamoDB\n- Riak\nDistributed Caches\n- Redis Clusters\n- Memcached Clusters\nLoad Balancing\n- Service routing\n- Request distribution\nCDNs\n- Edge server assignment",
      "autoResize": true,
      "lineHeight": 1.25
    },
    {
      "id": "0qe-r4S1VBZhUxIzBNEcO",
