    {
      "id": "uDg5iCwKkxBSwQMjhGjMy",
      "type": "text",
      "x": 1029.892822265625,
      "y": 1253.372802734375,
      "width": 227.93984985351562,
      "height": 200,
      "angle": 0,
      "strokeColor": "#1e1e1e",
      "backgroundColor": "#ffec99",
      "fillStyle": "solid",
      "strokeWidth": 2,
      "strokeStyle": "solid",
      "roughness": 1,
      "opacity": 100,
      "groupIds": [],
      "frameId": null,
      "index": "b3N",
      "roundness": null,
      "seed": 1871632410,
      "version": 95,
      "versionNonce": 1836003546,
      "isDeleted": true,
      "boundElements": null,
      "updated": 1781363287135,
      "link": null,
      "locked": false,
      "text": "For fault tolerance:\nReplication Factor = 3\n\nStore data on:\nPrimary Node\n+\nNext 2 clockwise nodes\n",
      "fontSize": 20,
      "fontFamily": 5,
      "textAlign": "left",
      "verticalAlign": "top",
      "containerId": null,
      "originalText": "For fault tolerance:\nReplication Factor = 3\n\nStore data on:\nPrimary Node\n+\nNext 2 clockwise nodes\n",
      "autoResize": true,
      "lineHeight": 1.25
    },
    {
      "id": "tEVSrMMXPh6x05rVHYLtx",
      "type": "text",
      "x": 574.0482177734375,
      "y": -2.196929931640625,
      "width": 740.9794921875,
      "height": 1025,
      "angle": 0,
      "strokeColor": "#1e1e1e",
      "backgroundColor": "transparent",
      "fillStyle": "solid",
      "strokeWidth": 2,
      "strokeStyle": "solid",
      "roughness": 1,
      "opacity": 100,
      "groupIds": [],
      "frameId": null,
      "index": "b3O",
      "roundness": null,
      "seed": 482870682,
      "version": 804,
      "versionNonce": 1517480198,
      "isDeleted": false,
      "boundElements": null,
      "updated": 1781364698771,
      "link": null,
      "locked": false,
      "text": "Unique ID generator\n\nQuestions?\n\nQ. Format of the ID?\nA. Numeric\n\nQ. Scale?\nA. 1000 ids per second\n\nQ. Multiple servers? how many?\nA. 100s\n\nQ. ANy specific req?\nA. ID should be within 64 bits of space\n\nFunctional Req:\n1. A system that generates unique IDs\n- Globally unique IDs\n- At very high scale\n- Across multiple servers\n- Without collisions\n\nNFR\n1. 1000s ids per second\n2. No duplicates\n3. Increment with time\n4. Low latency and highly available\n\nApproaches\n1. UUID ( 128 bits and alpha numeric)\n2. Increment id by number of servers ( not scalable)\n3. Create a server which creates ID and called by all other servers ( SPOF)\n4. Twitter snowflake approach\n\nSnowflake appoarch\n64 bits\n40 bits = ~34 years\n41 bits = ~69 years ( final)\n42 bits = ~139 years\n",
      "fontSize": 20,
      "fontFamily": 5,
      "textAlign": "left",
      "verticalAlign": "top",
      "containerId": null,
      "originalText": "Unique ID generator\n\nQuestions?\n\nQ. Format of the ID?\nA. Numeric\n\nQ. Scale?\nA. 1000 ids per second\n\nQ. Multiple servers? how many?\nA. 100s\n\nQ. ANy specific req?\nA. ID should be within 64 bits of space\n\nFunctional Req:\n1. A system that generates unique IDs\n- Globally unique IDs\n- At very high scale\n- Across multiple servers\n- Without collisions\n\nNFR\n1. 1000s ids per second\n2. No duplicates\n3. Increment with time\n4. Low latency and highly available\n\nApproaches\n1. UUID ( 128 bits and alpha numeric)\n2. Increment id by number of servers ( not scalable)\n3. Create a server which creates ID and called by all other servers ( SPOF)\n4. Twitter snowflake approach\n\nSnowflake appoarch\n64 bits\n40 bits = ~34 years\n41 bits = ~69 years ( final)\n42 bits = ~139 years\n",
      "autoResize": true,
      "lineHeight": 1.25
    },
