      "seed": 649315674,
      "version": 6,
      "versionNonce": 116738906,
      "isDeleted": false,
      "boundElements": null,
      "updated": 1781364844866,
      "link": null,
      "locked": false,
      "text": "# Clock Synchronization Problem\n\n## Issue\n\nSuppose server clock moves backward:\n\n```text\n10:00:05\n↓\n10:00:03\n```\n\nGenerated IDs may collide.\n\n### Solutions\n\n- Detect clock rollback\n- Pause ID generation\n- Use NTP synchronization\n- Alert operators\n",
      "fontSize": 20,
      "fontFamily": 5,
      "textAlign": "left",
      "verticalAlign": "top",
      "containerId": null,
      "originalText": "# Clock Synchronization Problem\n\n## Issue\n\nSuppose server clock moves backward:\n\n```text\n10:00:05\n↓\n10:00:03\n```\n\nGenerated IDs may collide.\n\n### Solutions\n\n- Detect clock rollback\n- Pause ID generation\n- Use NTP synchronization\n- Alert operators\n",
      "autoResize": true,
      "lineHeight": 1.25
    },
